    <abstract>
      <t>This memo describes an encapsulation method for carrying network interconnect traffic over a Frame Relay backbone.  It covers aspects of both Bridging and Routing.  Additionally, it describes a simple fragmentation procedure for carrying large frames over a frame relay network with a smaller MTU. [STANDARDS-TRACK]
